last_episode_to_air.overview: A wind of change is blowing in Seyong. Everyone has to choose what is most important and valuable.

name: RACE
overview: With little on her resume but full of passion, Park Yoonjo manages to get hired by a top company through an unbiased recruitment project. Proving her value at work is hard, but she powers through life with her old friend and colleague Ryu Jaemin, role model Goo Yijung, and best supporter Seo Donghoon.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: PR agency staff Yoon-jo gets a presentation chance from a top company, Seyong.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Yoon-jo's effort fails, and she moves on to another project. Seyong begins a new recruitment project.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Yoon-jo gets hired by Seyong through Spec-Out recruitment. The news of the new CCO makes a stir.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Yoonjo is busy with the promotion of Spec-Out. Soon, an article suspecting unfair hiring is posted.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Yoon-jo is assailed by doubts and Jae-min tries to reveal the truth. Yi-jung calls the PR department.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Jae-min is forced to assist Team 1. Yoon-jo takes on the cosmetics task and gets closer to Dong-hoon.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Yoon-jo's proposal for Celltics BI revamp shocks the company. She confesses her feelings to Jae-min.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Yoon-jo and Jae-min feel awkward in the TF team. Jae-min sees Dong-hoon confess his feelings to Yoon-jo.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: A negative publicity plan concerns Yoon-jo. The CEO's social media post undermines Yi-jung's position.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Negative publicity gets Yoon-jo in trouble. Jae-min finds faked data and is accused of whistleblowing.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Jae-min and Yoon-jo meet Yi-jung at the personnel committee. Meanwhile, Jae-min has confused emotions.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: A wind of change is blowing in Seyong. Everyone has to choose what is most important and valuable.
